## Component Integration

### ISystemComponent Interface

```python
class ISystemComponent(ABC):
    @abstractmethod
    async def initialize(self) -> bool: pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def start(self) -> bool: pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def stop(self) -> bool: pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def health_check(self) -> Dict[str, Any]: pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def configure_dependencies(self, orchestrator) -> bool: pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def prepare_for_shutdown(self) -> bool: pass
```

### Component Registration

```python
class MyComponent(ISystemComponent):
    def register_with_orchestrator(self, orchestrator: HierarchicalSystemOrchestrator):
        self.component_id = orchestrator.register_component(
            name="MyComponent",
            component=self,
            layer=ComponentLayer.EXECUTION,
            authority_level=AuthorityLevel.OPERATIONAL,
            initialization_order=20
        )
```

### Authorization Pattern

```python
async def request_operation_authorization(self, operation: str, details: Dict) -> bool:
    return await self.orchestrator.request_system_authorization(
        operation, self.component_id, details
    )
```

